    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/f19b4256a0c91b6a17b4455a545e2a83.poster.avif?t=1770836294\" width=800 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/f19b4256a0c91b6a17b4455a545e2a83.webm?t=1770836294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/f19b4256a0c91b6a17b4455a545e2a83.mp4?t=1770836294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Built to Hunt. Broken to Think.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Recycler. Your function is simple: track down war deserters. But when a highway explosion destroys your transport, it cracks your programming. Now trapped in the steel city of Sunket, you're experiencing a glitch of memories and voices. Find the truth before your makers decide you’ve learned too much.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Three Voices in Your Head</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your fractured consciousness is split into three voices. Decide which will lead your mind: deconstruct chaos with condescending logic, command every room with cold-blooded cool, or eavesdrop on the memories stained into the world. Let them guide you… or tear you in different directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/644242d7f6ae4cca6456812d87ec1088.poster.avif?t=1770836294\" width=804 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/644242d7f6ae4cca6456812d87ec1088.webm?t=1770836294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/644242d7f6ae4cca6456812d87ec1088.mp4?t=1770836294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Instrument That Whispers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>Listening Device</strong> is your guide. Use it to intercept hidden frequencies, uncover surface thoughts, and track electronic echoes. Follow the static trails to your next destination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/0b3645d6b1130c4b5d5e8652b6913369.poster.avif?t=1770836294\" width=804 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/0b3645d6b1130c4b5d5e8652b6913369.webm?t=1770836294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082700/extras/0b3645d6b1130c4b5d5e8652b6913369.mp4?t=1770836294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sunket: A City on the Brink</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Workers vanish inside the factories. Smoke chokes the streets. The city’s leaders are unraveling, and something whispers from beneath the pavement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive, uncover who targeted your transport. <strong>When your makers learn you’ve awakened, will you remain a tool... or become something they fear?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
